OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777468272
OL,3,CBrighton announce plans for Europe's
OL,4,Cfirst purpose-built women's football
OL,5,Cground
OL,7,FBrighton and Hove Albion F.C. have
OL,8,Fannounced plans for Europe's first
OL,9,Fpurpose-built women's football stadium.
OL,11,FThe stadium, which would have a
OL,12,Fminimum capacity of 10,000, would be
OL,13,Fbuilt on a site known as Bennett's
OL,14,FField, near to the Amex Stadium which
OL,15,Fis home to Brighton's men's team.
OL,17,FIt will be physically connected to the
OL,18,FAmex by a new bridge link.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
