FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777468272
OL,3,CBrighton announce plans for Europe's
OL,4,Cfirst purpose-built women's football
OL,5,Cground
OL,7,FWork has begun on a planning
OL,8,Fapplication for the Bennett's Field
OL,9,Fsite, which the club bought in 2025.
OL,11,FThe Seagulls say that the stadium will
OL,12,Fopen no later than the 2030/31 season,
OL,13,Fsubject to planning approvals from
OL,14,FBrighton and Hove City Council and
OL,15,FLewes District Council.
OL,17,FThe club say that the stadium will
OL,18,Fprovide a permanent home and identity
OL,19,Ffor the women's team, which a focus on
OL,20,Fsupporting elite female players in
OL,21,Fevery element of the design.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777468272
OL,3,CBrighton announce plans for Europe's
OL,4,Cfirst purpose-built women's football
OL,5,Cground
OL,7,FThe club added that significant
OL,8,Fprogress has been made on design work
OL,9,Ffor the stadium.
OL,11,FThey emphasised that the stadium would
OL,12,Ffollow the motto 'built for her', with
OL,13,Fa strong focus on meeting the
OL,14,F"distinct needs and requirements of
OL,15,Fthe women's game."
OL,17,FThey hope that the new stadium will
OL,18,Fattract new fans and be welcoming for
OL,19,Ffamilies and first time attendees.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777468272
OL,3,CBrighton announce plans for Europe's
OL,4,Cfirst purpose-built women's football
OL,5,Cground
OL,7,FBrighton are currently in sixth place
OL,8,Fin the Women's Super League.
OL,10,FWomen's managing director Zoe Johnson
OL,11,Fsaid, "The prospect of a bespoke
OL,12,Fstadium, built exclusively for women's
OL,13,Fplayers, staff and supporters, is
OL,14,Fincredibly exciting.
OL,16,F"It is a project that is the first of
OL,17,Fits kind in the UK and Europe, and one
OL,18,Fof only three in the world, and will
OL,19,Fcapture the imagination of
OL,20,Fstakeholders across the women's game,
OL,21,Fnot just here but globally.
OL,26,@sD@GOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777468272
OL,3,CBrighton announce plans for Europe's
OL,4,Cfirst purpose-built women's football
OL,5,Cground
OL,7,F"It is something we are asked about
OL,8,Fconstantly, and we have worked hard to
OL,9,Freach this moment, so it is exciting
OL,10,Fnow to share this news with the wider
OL,11,Fworld.
OL,13,Ft will help us push forward our
OL,14,Fambitions to compete consistently both
OL,15,Fdomestically in the Women's Super
OL,16,FLeague, and also in European club
OL,17,Fcompetition while helping us to
OL,18,Fattract key staff and grow a
OL,19,Fpassionate fan base.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
