PN,41606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777468272
OL,3,CBrighton announce plans for Europe's
OL,4,Cfirst purpose-built women's football
OL,5,Cground
OL,7,F"We also hope the stadium can support
OL,8,Facademy and development fixtures,
OL,9,Fgiving more of our younger players
OL,10,Fvaluable experience of playing in a
OL,11,Fpurpose-built stadium environment."
OL,13,FChair of Albion Women Michelle Walder
OL,14,Fadded, "We are determined to maintain
OL,15,Fthe momentum built in recent years,
OL,16,Fnot just nationally but here in the
OL,17,Fcity.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@cO]vD@HOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
