PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777468272
OL,3,CBrighton announce plans for Europe's
OL,4,Cfirst purpose-built women's football
OL,5,Cground
OL,7,F"A stadium 'built for her' is an
OL,8,Fambitious statement of intent ` it's
OL,9,Fan exciting commitment and will
OL,10,Festablish Brighton and Hove on the
OL,11,Fglobal map as a genuine home for the
OL,12,Fwomen's game. Delivering these plans
OL,13,Fis central to accelerating the
OL,14,Flongterm growth of our women's team
OL,15,Fand the future of the wider game."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
