PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777468272
OL,3,CBrighton announce plans for Europe's
OL,4,Cfirst purpose-built women's football
OL,5,Cground
OL,7,FAlbion chairman Tony Bloom said,
OL,8,F"Since we announced our intention to
OL,9,Fbuild a stadium for the women's team
OL,10,Fin Brighton and Hove, we have seen
OL,11,Funprecedented interest locally,
OL,12,Fnationally and internationally.
OL,14,F"It is a topic I am regularly asked
OL,15,Fabout by many of our fans, clearly
OL,16,Findicating the growing level of
OL,17,Finterest and potential for women's
OL,18,Ffootball.
OL,26,@pD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
