PN,41609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1777468272
OL,3,CBrighton announce plans for Europe's
OL,4,Cfirst purpose-built women's football
OL,5,Cground
OL,7,F"It is a significant further
OL,8,Finvestment in our long term vision for
OL,9,Fwomen's football at Brighton & Hove
OL,10,FAlbion. A women's stadium in the city
OL,11,Fis essential to the continued growth
OL,12,Fof the team"
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
